		{
			description: [
				"[gap=3]"
				"&b&lHostile Neural Networks&r"
				"[gap=2]"
				"also known here as.."
				"[gap=2]"
				"## &4&lDrygmy Farm Successor&r"
				"[gap=0]"
				"---"
				"[gap=4]"
				"This mod lets you to capture a &2mob&r train him in a &especial item&r and after that produce the &eloot&r of this &2mob&r."
				"It's actually really simple but i'll guide you through it anyway!"
				"[spoiler]Well.. I have to."
				"[gap=3]"
			]
